  "description": [
    "trying to talk to the general about it now though Come to dinner tonight Hell be a lot easier to talk to after hes had his second martini Dinner Dusty mumbled l happen to be his daughter Pat said Con aider yourself invited Leave that cat at home It was after seven when Dusty parked his car in the generals driveway He was late and also badly worried because he hadnt been able to find General Kong before he left The general must have gotten out somehow and while he might be at home in the jungles of Vietnam Washington D C was something else again Pat answered the door Dads in the study she said Thank goodness you left that cat at home Hes lost Dusty said glumly In the study Hobnails Hardwick shook his hand gave him a martini and glowered at him So you want to go back to Vietnam he demanded Why Dusty told him why but his heart wasnt in it now He kept thinking of Kong wander ing around lost and alone Once he thought he heard that familiar yowl then decided it was wishful thinking He concluded his plea feeling that it wasnt"
  ],
